OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FRomeo Beckham had a run-in with the
OL,7,Fpolice after he was caught scrolling
OL,8,Fon his phone at the wheel of his
OL,9,FPorsche 911 ` with a dog loose in the
OL,10,Fcar.
OL,12,FThe 23-year-old model was pulled over
OL,13,Fin Westminster last September after a
OL,14,Fpolice officer spotted him with both
OL,15,Fhands on his phone instead of the
OL,16,Fsteering wheel while at a red light.
OL,18,FA woman was in the passenger seat also
OL,19,Flooking at her phone and with an
OL,20,F"unrestrained" dog in her lap, court
OL,21,Fpapers reveal.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
