OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FIn a statement, the officer said
OL,7,FBeckham was "distracted" and did not
OL,8,Fhave proper control of the supercar.
OL,10,FAt Westminster Magistrates' Court last
OL,11,FThursday, Beckham was convicted of
OL,12,Fbeing a driver not in a position to
OL,13,Fhave proper control, and issued with a
OL,14,F#440 fine with three penalty points
OL,15,Ffor his licence.
OL,17,FHe was also ordered by magistrate
OL,18,FPhillip Jordan to pay #130 in costs
OL,19,Fand a #176 victim surcharge.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
