OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FThe court case comes almost exactly
OL,7,Fseven years since his father, Sir
OL,8,FDavid Beckham, was banned from driving
OL,9,Ffor six months for using his mobile
OL,10,Fphone at the wheel.
OL,12,FIn that 2019 case, the former
OL,13,Ffootballer admitted being on his phone
OL,14,Fin slow moving traffic in the West
OL,15,FEnd, and told a court he would miss
OL,16,Fdriving his children ` Romeo, then 16,
OL,17,FCruz, then 14, and Harper, then seven
OL,18,F` to school while serving the ban.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FRomeo Beckham, the second son of David
OL,7,Fand Victoria Beckham, was caught out
OL,8,Fby Metropolitan Police Pc Luke Short
OL,9,Fon September 16 last year, while
OL,10,Fwaiting at a red traffic light in
OL,11,FVictoria Street, Westminster, just
OL,12,Fbefore 11.20am.
OL,14,FThe officer said he passed the Porsche
OL,15,F911 Carrera and assessed the driver as
OL,16,Fbeing "distracted" due to the scene
OL,17,Finside.
OL,26,@xD@GOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,F"As I passed the vehicle on its
OL,7,Fnearside, I looked down to my right
OL,8,Fand noted that there was an
OL,9,Funrestrained dog sitting on the female
OL,10,Fpassenger's lap," he wrote in his
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,F"The female had her head down and was
OL,14,Fholding a mobile phone.
OL,16,F"I looked across at the driver. I saw
OL,17,Fthat he too had his head tilted down
OL,18,Fand appeared to be looking down at a
OL,19,Fmobile phone he was holding low in his
OL,20,Flap, near the base of the steering
OL,21,Fwheel.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]uD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,F"I could see that he was scrolling on
OL,7,Fthe device with his thumbs."
OL,9,FThe officer pulled Beckham over and
OL,10,Fconfronted him, and said he decided to
OL,11,Fuse his discretion to offer the driver
OL,12,F"words of advice concerning the
OL,13,Finsecure load, namely the dog".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@\O]tD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FRule 57 of the Highway Code sets out
OL,7,Fthat dogs must be "suitably
OL,8,Frestrained" in a vehicle, and the
OL,9,Fdriver can be prosecuted for driving
OL,10,Fwithout proper control or careless
OL,11,Fdriving if it is assessed the animal
OL,12,Fis causing a distraction or affecting
OL,13,Fthe quality of the driving.
OL,15,FBeckham's brush with the law came days
OL,16,Fafter he had debuted a new platinum
OL,17,Fblonde buzzcut at a New York Fashion
OL,18,FWeek event.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
