OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FTwo days after the incident, Beckham
OL,7,Fmade his runway debut at London
OL,8,FFashion Week at the H&M show.
OL,10,FPolice say he was given the chance to
OL,11,Fpay a fine and go on a driver
OL,12,Fawareness course to avoid criminal
OL,13,Fproceedings over using his phone in
OL,14,Fthe car, but he did not respond to the
OL,15,Foffer.
OL,17,FBeckham was then prosecuted through
OL,18,Fthe single justice procedure, which
OL,19,Fhandles driving offences in private
OL,20,Fhearings.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
