OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781783277
OL,3,CRomeo Beckham charged over phone use
OL,4,Cand loose dog in Porsche
OL,6,FThe court said Beckham did not enter a
OL,7,Fplea to the charge when written to at
OL,8,Fhis luxury south-west London
OL,9,Fapartment, and he was convicted on the
OL,10,Fbasis of the police evidence on
OL,11,FThursday last week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
